Services

Yes, we do that.

Need to sell your house?

Wheter it's a new job and you need to move now or you simply need out due to financial reasons, we've got you covered. We use cash lenders and can have you paid within hours, not days.

We Pay Cash

While we offer other services depending on your situation, but if you're looking for immediate cash, we have access to hundres of lenders that are ready to write you a check for your home.

Looking for Investment Property

Wheter you're an experienced investor that knows what they want or your're a new investor insterested in 15% returns on your capital, we've got you covered. Are you looking for a better investment than your savings account? Do 12-15% returns sound better than what you're getting on your current investments? We have access to hundres of investment properties throughout the greater Kansas City area and can help guide you through the process of becoming a real estate investor.

We've got what you need!

Whether you're looking to sell your home or buy an investment property, we've got you covered.

Get Started!

How It Works

You are four steps away from cash in hand.

  • 1

    Enter your basic property information.

    Send us a message with your property information. We respond immediately.

  • 2

    We'll arrange a time to view your home.

    You're busy. We get it. We will work with your schedule in order to make things as easy as possible for you.

  • 3

    Get a no-obligation, cash offer. No repairs needed.

    Whether your property is in perfect shape or is in need of new carpet, appliances, plumbing, or foundation work, we've got you covered. No property is too nice or too ugly for us.

  • 4

    If you accept - we'll buy your house quickly and hassle free.

    If you accept our offer, you get paid today. The check is in your hand as fast as the title company can write it.
